subject: Dear Sir/Ma
body:
Dear Sir/Ma
I am MR.Samuel Williams a consultant/broker, we consult/broker for a
consortium of investment companies. Our investment partners are
looking at investing in viable projects in different sectors on a loan
basis. If interested, reach out to me and I shall give you more
insight on how we will proceed towards a conclusion of the process.
Looking forward to hearing from you.
Regards,
MR.Samuel Williams
Principal Consultant

subject: Re: Dear Sir/Ma
body:
Hello Williams, thank you for reaching out. I'm interested in learning more about the investment opportunities your consortium is considering. Could you provide some examples of the sectors and types of projects that your partners are looking to invest in? I look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Kelly
